GBQualifier.GBQualifier_value: Long PCR amplified, re-cloned 9kb fragment from infectious HIV-1 clone pNL4-3, subclone 4.20. Insert sequence only, vector is pNOTA. Cloned into Invitrogen vector pNOTA from extended PCR amplification product using original pNL4-3 molecular clone as template. Only 17 mutations compared to original published sequence (GenBank Accession Number M19921) were observed.
